{"tid":1565320,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"跳閳是不是犧牲太多？是不是應該改變一下策略？","createTime":"2019-09-13T05:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T11:30:44.000Z","uid":158408,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"80cf0b2fa9024e2a9b7051ca9a3063c94e973eab","tid":1565320,"uid":158408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"我個人唔反對跳閳，我自己都跳過。但敵人改變手法，我們是否應該變陣？<br />\n<br />\n我自己幾次都見到狗鐡請左好多人，去捉人。<br />\n第二跳閳不停比藍絲廢老，話我地食霸王餐。<br />\n<br />\n現在跳閳罰$5000，重要班黨鐵報警比狗拉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n杯葛 mtr 廣告供應商？<br />\n<br />\n當然大家確保安全，我唔反對大家跳，兄弟爬山各有各做<br />\n<br />\n但好似我見到粉衫就唔夠膽跳的廢柴，大家可否幫我一些建議如何何抵制黨鐡<br />\n<br />\n如果有更好的策略，大家可否建議一下？"},{"pid":"4e423d311a771562adc4381b9d25abf8765b1571","tid":1565320,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:58:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"095d55bb66499bd865744a2a413fca78098b1d9d","tid":1565320,"uid":158408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:23:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44226c78de9d4da796b7c36e62bb9dfd0ef6875a","tid":1565320,"uid":85358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"打工仔記得轉走強積金！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565101</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">推一推比多啲人見到，強積金係大家血汗錢，唔可以就咁蝕曬佢！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人未轉（我公司班人都係啱啱轉）<br />\n趁依家股市托高咗，記得叫埋家人同事一齊轉！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">轉買債劵/美股都好</span></span></strong><br />\n覺得中美和好可以買多少少美股<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我自己就轉買債多</span></strong>"},{"pid":"73076573637197967560d8a7011e3df3442982b1","tid":1565320,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">柒婆回應係<br />\n佢唔止要撤回送中 <br />\n佢仲要撤回四大訴求</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你唔妥協 就要升級！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【913升級? 升撚咗去邊】<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>914 915 拆鐵! ⚑</strong></span></span> <br />\n個個站都要人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1564098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1564098</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lw92QGB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLw92QGB.jpg&h=876e10b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a38b78f995fba6e88c5cf749fa39e93f66b72b9","tid":1565320,"uid":36849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:32:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c51f473bc5515822f5533aeddfb7dd73f9cfa0bf","tid":1565320,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"其實宜家跳閘開始唔化算<br />\n第一佢地已經請左一大班人黎睇閘口<br />\n又有藍絲同便衣狗幫忙<br />\n當平均每程收費 $10 即係多過 2%失敗率被捉罰 $500 已經失敗"},{"pid":"f1835709d7fe53b5d2e0ee8222157eefb65f7f85","tid":1565320,"uid":218865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:52:05.000Z",